title: Best of Clancy And The Rockets Week 3: Christian Yelich Calls In, Marty Mush Makes Out, Hatfished, and Ellie vs. Francis
description:
Last week on Clancy and the Rockets (LIVE everyday on Barstool Radio SiriusXM Channel 85 from 1pm-3pm) we had the freshly crown NL MVP Christian Yelich (9:12) called in.
